    "name": "鬼灵双盗",
    "steam_appid": 1709870,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1709870/extras/741d6a7cb6579f78b3c18abf261cc79d.avif?t=1737635238\" width=600 height=66 /></span><br><br><strong>鬼灵双盗 </strong>是一款别具一格的回合制战术潜行游戏。慢慢侦察前面的路，让幽灵朋友来策划抢劫，然后利用你的知识闯入金库，卷走价格昂贵的宝石悄然离开吧。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1709870/extras/f37a3354b9cd408b253a163ec102dc93.poster.avif?t=1737635238\" width=582 height=347 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1709870/extras/f37a3354b9cd408b253a163ec102dc93.webm?t=1737635238\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>又一次任务出了岔子……伊莱贾，这个不走运的小偷在魔术方面倒是有两把刷子；崔林，伊莱贾的犯罪同伙，还碰巧是个无形的鬼魂——两人离被踢出无情的盗贼工会，就差那么一丁点！<br><br>伊莱贾和崔林下定决心要向工会证明自己，顺便在途中顺手牵羊小赚一把，因此必须齐心协力，潜入守卫森严的宝库、神秘的墓穴乃至更多地方。在偶尔还有盟友出手相助的这一路冒险上，这个组合究竟会遇上什么样的秘密、宝藏和麻烦呢？<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1709870/extras/6b2fb195f7c3f7c436da5f47e45247c5.avif?t=1737635238\" width=600 height=66 /></span><br><br>以幽灵崔林的身份，神不知鬼不觉地<strong>侦察</strong>敌情。探索、策划、定位秘密通道和隐藏宝藏，没了身子，一身轻松。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1709870/extras/07b906393b6eba1b221b32d8cb2fff49.poster.avif?t=1737635238\" width=582 height=339 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1709870/extras/07b906393b6eba1b221b32d8cb2fff49.webm?t=1737635238\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>以窃贼伊莱贾的身份盗窃。拼命掠夺财宝，别给守卫留反应的时间。<br></li><li>智取敌人，潜入上锁的门，并打破魔法屏障。没有哪扇门能阻止你前进的脚步。<br></li><li>在回合制的游戏玩法下闯入又闯出，别让守卫留意到你的存在。时间只有这么多，务必明智使用你的回合。</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1709870/extras/78551e4a3f4716ad0eca8cd9f1314229.avif?t=1737635238\" width=600 height=66 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>在臭名昭著的盗贼公会指引下，潜入富裕的城堡、暗黑的地牢以及神秘的巢穴。<br></li><li>升级技能，用不义之财换取激动人心的全新能力。<br></li><li>研究传达的指示，以便掌握接下来要面对的状况和要寻找的东西。你是打算慢慢来、稳步寻得所有秘密呢，还是说拿了就跑更对你胃口？</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1709870/extras/6c498cdef82d4f22583301c6ced53ae0.poster.avif?t=1737635238\" width=582 height=351 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1709870/extras/6c498cdef82d4f22583301c6ced53ae0.webm?t=1737635238\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span>",
